episodes.title: We were brainwashed into working for a sales cult
episodes.description: In an exclusive investigation, WalesOnline Investigations Editor Conor Gogarty uncovers disturbing practices and cult-like methods at a network of sales offices. Credico reportedly has around 100 sales offices linked to it in the UK, including Cardiff. Full report on WalesOnline https://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/we-were-brainwashed-working-sales-29288752
